{"tid":1077273,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"廚房佬入嚟","createTime":"2019-03-25T12:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T06:29:26.000Z","uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4679ade7131d4fb6ed72737d73be4a9a3a1eb17","tid":1077273,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"人在異鄉 啲鬼見我唐人樣 請咗我做廚房佬煮小炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家日日畀件鬼婆教我炒唐餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己對呢方面好有興趣 平時都有喺屋企鳩整畀自己食 但零做廚經驗 只係有刨過兩登廚房佬啲post （所以大概知件鬼婆啲手勢唔撚係路 啲嘢似樣就算）<br />\n老細叫我跟佢兩個禮拜 之後就畀我自己做 到時甚至menu都肯畀我度<br />\n我唔想學壞手勢 同時想將港式廚房佬文化宣揚 <br />\n有冇廚房佬分享吓啲實冇死嘅gesture同概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如猛/陰鑊同油嘅關係、飛水/走油嘅應用、啲嘢擺位、身體點用力、清潔步驟呢啲<br />\n<br />\n廚房佬呢個term冇貶義 純粹覺得咁樣先突顯到中廚嗰份麻甩豪爽味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6463509a7d5666c84a33e03f82c54ebf9e5c5903","tid":1077273,"uid":48286,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"Cls 講幾句你就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c1b253a95151f2ed814cbbce82f81ae652d94d","tid":1077273,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6463509a7d5666c84a33e03f82c54ebf9e5c5903","tid":1077273,"uid":48286,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"Cls 講幾句你就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"當然冇可能 <br />\n所以純粹想喺度請教巴打有咩gesture/concept係基本實冇死得嚟又好撚緊要"},{"pid":"9d382cbceab451532f31640be508f8949a070115","tid":1077273,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"人地正正經經拜師都要洗兩年碗先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43871261c8a66a5ec9d7c72261d0825e6db44c64","tid":1077273,"uid":69994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"sc